\c 23
\p
\v 1 Zvino Bharamu wakati kuna Bharaki: Ndivakire pano aritari nomwe, ugondigadzirire pano nzombe nomwe nemakondohwe manomwe\x + 23.29. 1 Makor. 15.26. Job. 42.8.\x*.
\v 2 Bharaki ndokuita Bharamu sezvaakataura; Bharaki naBharamu ndokupa nzombe diki negondohwe\x + 23.4,14,30.\x* paaritari \add imwe neimwe\add*.
\v 3 Zvino Bharamu wakati kuna Bharaki: Mira pachipo chako chinopiswa\x + 23.15.\x*, asi ini ndichaenda; zvimwe Jehovha achauya kuzosangana neni; zvino chinhu chaanondiratidza ndichakuudza\x + 24.1.\x*. Zvino wakaenda pakakwirira.
\v 4 Zvino Mwari wakasangana naBharamu\x + 23.16.\x*, \add iye\add* ndokuti kwaari: Ndagadzira aritari nomwe uye ndapa nzombe diki negondohwe paaritari \add imwe neimwe.\add*
\v 5 Jehovha ndokuisa shoko mumuromo waBharamu, ndokuti: Dzokera kuna Bharaki ugotaura seizvi\x + 22.38; 23.12,16. Isa. 51.16; 59.21. Det. 18.18. Jer. 1.9.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino wakadzokera kwaari, uye tarira, amire pachipo chake chinopiswa, iye nemachinda ose aMoabhu.
\v 7 Zvino wakasimudza mufananidzo wake ndokuti: Bharaki mambo waMoabhu wakandivinga kubva Siriya, pamakomo ekumabvazuva \add achiti\x + 23.18; 24.3,15,20,23; 21.27.\x*\add*: Uya nditukire Jakove\x + 22.6.\x*, uye uya unyombe Israeri\x + Isa. 66.14. Mara. 1.4.\x*.
\v 8 Ini ndingatuka sei\x + 22.11,17.\x* Mwari waasina kutuka\x + 22.11,17.\x*; uye ndinganyomba sei Jehovha waasina kunyomba?
\v 9 Nokuti kubva panhongonya yemabwe ndinomuona, uye kubva pazvikomo ndinomutarisa; tarira, vanhu vachagara vega\x + Det. 33.28.\x*, uye havangaverengwi pakati pendudzi\x + Eki. 33.16. Ezi. 9.2. VaEfe. 2.14.\x*.
\v 10 Ndiani angaverenga guruva raJakove\x + Gen. 13.16.\x*, nekuverenga chechina chaIsraeri? Mweya wangu ngaufe rufu rwevakarurama\x + Map. 116.15.\x*, uye magumo angu ngaave seake!
\v 11 Zvino Bharaki wakati kuna Bharamu: Wandiitei? Ndakutora kuti utuke vavengi vangu; zvino tarira, wa\add va\add*ropafadza neku\add va\add*ropafadza\x + 22.11,17; 24.10. Det. 23.5.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino wakapindura ndokuti: Handifaniri kuchenjerera kutaura izvo Jehovha zvaanoisa mumuromo mangu here\x + 22.38. 23.5.\x*?
\v 13 Zvino Bharaki wakati kwaari: Uya hako neni kune imwe nzvimbo paungavaona kubvapo; uchaona kuguma kwavo chete, uye haungavaoni vose; ugonditukira ivo kubva ipapo.
\p
\v 14 Zvino wakamutora akamuisa mumunda weZofimu, panhongonya yePisiga, ndokuvaka aritari nomwe, ndokupa nzombe diki negondohwe paaritari \add imwe neimwe\x + 23.1,2.\x*\add*.
\v 15 Zvino wakati kuna Bharaki: Mira pano pachipo chako chinopiswa, zvino ini ndichasangana na\add Jehovha\add* uko\x + 23.3,4,16.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino Jehovha wakasangana naBharamu, ndokuisa shoko mumuromo make\x + 22.35. 23.5.\x*, ndokuti: Dzokera kuna Bharaki ugotaura seizvi.
\v 17 Zvino asvika kwaari, tarira, amire pachipo chake chinopiswa, nemachinda aMoabhu anaye. Bharaki ndokuti kwaari: Jehovha wataurei?
\v 18 Zvino wakasimudza mufananidzo wake ndokuti: Simuka Bharaki, ugonzwa; urereke nzeve kwandiri, iwe mwanakomana waZipori:
\v 19 Mwari haasi munhu kuti areve nhema\x + 1 Zvak. 15.29. Mara. 3.6. VaRom. 11.29. Tit. 1.2. Jak. 1.17.\x*, kana mwanakomana wemunhu kuti ashanduke. Iye wakareva, haangaiti kanhi? Kana wakareva, haangasimbisi kanhi?
\v 20 Tarira, ndagamuchira kuti ndiropafadze; zvino waropafadza, uye handigoni kuzvidzosa\x + 22.12. Gen. 12.3; 22.17.\x*.
\v 21 Haana kutarisira chakaipa kuna Jakove; uye haana kuona kutsauka kuna Israeri\x + Job. 4.8; 15.35. Map. 7.14; 10.7,14,.\x*; Jehovha Mwari wake anaye, nekudanidzira kwamambo kuri pakati pavo\x + Map. 89.15.\x*.
\v 22 Mwari wakavabudisa Egipita\x + 24.8.\x*, ane sesimba renyati\x + Det. 33.17. Map. 29.6; 92.10. Isa. 34.7. Job. 39.10,11. Map. 22.21.\x*\x + Job. 22.25. Map. 95.4.\x*.
\v 23 Zvirokwazvo hakuna un'anga hunopikisa Jakove, kana kuvuka kunopikisa Israeri\x + Det. 18.10. 22.7.\x*. Ikozvino zvicharehwa pamusoro paJakove nepamusoro paIsraeri kuti Mwari wakazviita\x + Map. 44.1.\x*.
\v 24 Tarirai, vanhu vachasimuka seshumbakadzi\x + Gen. 49.9.\x*, vazvisimudze seshumba\x + Gen. 49.9.\x*. Havangarari pasi kusvika vadya chakajimbiwa, uye vanwa ropa revakaurawa\x + Gen. 49.27.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Zvino Bharaki wakati kuna Bharamu: Zvino usatongovatuka kana kutongovaropafadza.
\v 26 Asi Bharamu wakapindura, ndokuti kuna Bharaki: Handina kukuudza here ndichiti: Zvose Jehovha zvaanotaura, ndizvo zvandichaita\x + 22.18.\x*?
\p
\v 27 Zvino Bharaki wakati kuna Bharamu: Uya hako, ndichakuendesa kune imwe nzvimbo\x + 23.13.\x*; zvimwe zvingarurama pameso aMwari kuti unditukire ivo kubva ipapo.
\v 28 Zvino Bharaki wakatora ndokuisa Bharamu panhongonya yePeori\x + 25.18; 31.16. Josh. 22.17. 25.3,5. Det. 4.3. Map. 106.28. Hos. 9.10.\x*, pakatarisa pasi pachiso cherenje\x + 21.20.\x*.
\v 29 Zvino Bharamu wakati kuna Bharaki: Ndivakire pano aritari nomwe, undigadzirire pano nzombe diki nomwe nemakondohwe manomwe\x + 23.1,2.\x*.
\v 30 Bharaki ndokuita Bharamu sezvaakataura, ndokupa nzombe diki negondohwe paaritari \add imwe neimwe\x + 23.1,2.\x*\add*.
